FAILED_NO_SIGNATURE - Enum constant in enum class io.dimeformat.keyring.IntegrityState

FAILED_NOT_TRUSTED - Enum constant in enum class io.dimeformat.keyring.IntegrityState

FAILED_USED_BEFORE_ISSUED - Enum constant in enum class io.dimeformat.keyring.IntegrityState
